        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2005123653" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3336237231963564745">2.5*<br/><br/>The writing style is very good. However the pacing is super slow. If you&apos;re going to have a slow pace, for me, you have to balance it with some sort of engaging psychological gauging of the characters usually with a high dose of empathy or some type of theoretical discussion which is thought provoking or some witty character banter. <br/><br/>I think if you like old school fantasy and it&apos;s pacing you&apos;ll love this. If you don&apos;t then not so much. </span>
  <span id="freeText3336237231963564745" style="display:none">2.5*<br /><br />The writing style is very good. However the pacing is super slow. If you're going to have a slow pace, for me, you have to balance it with some sort of engaging psychological gauging of the characters usually with a high dose of empathy or some type of theoretical discussion which is thought provoking or some witty character banter. <br /><br />I think if you like old school fantasy and it's pacing you'll love this. If you don't then not so much. </span>
